Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:18.22,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}natsukashii bamen hodoite koboshita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:23.69,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}eranda ketsui wo shimetsukeru paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:29.24,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}todokanai asu ni shizumeta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:35.53,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nigirishimeru kono te wo hirakeba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:43.63,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}furete shimau tou ni nageta kibou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:49.71,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}namida wo karashi mukau kono yami wo nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:55.85,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}tsutsuganai mirai anata ga mitsumeteitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:01.18,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}yatto yatto tsukami kaketa hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}daremo nanimo iwanakute ii
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:16.57,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}subete no kotae wa koko ni chanto aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.55,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}As cores se espalham até onde o olhar alcança,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:18.22,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma cena nostálgica se desenrola e se espalham.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:23.69,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um paradoxo que confunde nossas decisões,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:29.24,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}afundado em um amanhã inalcançável.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:35.53,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Se eu abrir essa mão que seguro com força,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:43.63,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}poderei alcançar a esperança que abandonei há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:49.71,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Enxugue suas lágrimas e siga em frente para romper esta escuridão.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:55.85,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Mesmo quando você olha para um futuro sem esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:01.18,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Eu finalmente, finalmente, comecei a entender a luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.15,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Não é preciso dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:16.57,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Porque todas as respostas estão bem aqui.
