Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:12.94,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}atarimae no you ni sugite iku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:19.28,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nanige nai shiawase mitsukete wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:24.91,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}toikakete kurukawaita kaze ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:30.46,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}fuwari mau hana hitohira
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:42.80,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}itsuka itsuka to himeru awaku senmei na kage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:49.35,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}mada koko de iki wo surukarenu itami to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:58.61,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}anata wo matsu sore dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:17.25,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nanige nai shiawase ikiru kono sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:12.94,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Tudo se foi tão naturalmente,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:19.28,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}buscando uma simples felicidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:24.91,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}No vento seco que me desafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:30.46,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma única flor voando.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:42.80,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um dia, em algum lugar, a sombra tênue e radiante se esconderá.
